---
title: Everything Bagel Avocado Toasts with Balsamic Mixed Greens & Grape Tomatoes
description: Here’s a simple, delicious plant-based meal that will surely become a lunchtime staple. Why? It just takes a few minutes to throw together, and it’s got all the flavors and textures to qualify for a supremely satisfying and wholesome midday fuel-up. It starts with chewy toasted sourdough bread you’ll spread with a layer of guacamole blended with olive oil and everything bagel seasoning for crisp little pops of umami-saltiness. A crisp mixed green salad with juicy grape tomatoes and tangy balsamic glaze is piled over the top. That’s right, you’re just 15 minutes from total lunchtime bliss!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651320e7b6b74f3addadb4f5-c01c25f4.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/651320e7b6b74f3addadb4f5.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/everything-bagel-avocado-toasts-651320e7b6b74f3addadb4f5
time required: 15 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 430 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 4 g
  carbohydrates: 68 g
  sugar: 10 g
